            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Rtps is good till 8th .won't suggest any parent to send their children who r studying BTW 9 - 12th std . Pathetic pressure on students .unnecessary  exams being conducted even when the portion isn't completed . My brother who just passed out 12th he also said the same thing that the school was good till 8th std . U will spoil ur life if u study for 9 th ,  10th,11th and 12th in this school. And those guys who are going to take integrated take it at ur own risk. wud suggest the parents that if their  child opts for jee/ neet go for other coaching classes like Allen or pw but pls don't put them in the coaching class which has tied up with rtps. If u touch the smart board also u wud b landing to the principals office . I mean what the hell.  Just bcos we touched a smart board v will be punished .",
